### FitScore API Test File
### Usar con REST Client (VS Code) o IntelliJ IDEA

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================
### HEALTH & STATUS
### ============================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### API Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/status

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================

### Login (obtener token) - Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123

### Login JSON alternativo
# @name loginJson
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login/json
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Guardar token de la respuesta anterior
@authToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.access_token}}

### Ver usuario actual
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Listar usuarios (solo admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crear nuevo usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "juez1",
  "password": "juez123",
  "email": "juez1@fitscore.com",
  "full_name": "Juez Primero",
  "role": "judge"
}

### ============================================
### COMPETITIONS
### ============================================

### Listar competencias
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crear competencia
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "CrossFit Open 2024",
  "date": "2024-03-15",
  "location": "Box Central",
  "description": "Competencia anual de CrossFit",
  "is_active": true
}

### Ver competencia especifica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Actualizar competencia
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "CrossFit Open 2024 - Actualizado",
  "is_active": true
}

### Dashboard de competencia
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions/1/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Recalcular rankings y puntos de una competencia
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions/1/recalculate
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### ATHLETES
### ============================================

### Listar atletas de competencia
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions/1/athletes
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crear atleta
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/athletes
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "competition_id": 1,
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "email": "juan@email.com",
  "bib_number": "101",
  "division": "RX Masculino",
  "box": "CrossFit Norte",
  "age": 28,
  "gender": "M"
}

### Ver atleta
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/athletes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Actualizar atleta
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/athletes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Juan Perez Garcia",
  "box": "CrossFit Sur"
}

### Descargar template CSV para importar atletas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/export/1/athletes/template
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Importar atletas desde CSV (usar form-data)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions/1/athletes/import
# Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
#
# --boundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="atletas.csv"
# Content-Type: text/csv
#
# name,email,bib_number,division,box,age,gender
# Maria Lopez,maria@email.com,102,RX Femenino,Box Central,25,F
# --boundary--

### ============================================
### WODs
### ============================================

### Listar WODs de competencia
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/competitions/1/wods
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crear WOD tipo TIME (For Time)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/wods
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "competition_id": 1,
  "name": "WOD 5 - Fran",
  "description": "21-15-9 Thrusters y Pull-ups",
  "wod_type": "TIME",
  "time_cap": 600,
  "order_in_competition": 5
}

### Crear WOD tipo AMRAP
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/wods
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "competition_id": 1,
  "name": "WOD 6 - AMRAP 12",
  "description": "12 min AMRAP: 10 Box Jumps, 10 KB Swings",
  "wod_type": "AMRAP",
  "time_cap": 720,
  "order_in_competition": 6
}

### Crear WOD tipo LOAD (max weight)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/wods
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "competition_id": 1,
  "name": "WOD 7 - Max Clean",
  "description": "Encontrar 1RM Clean",
  "wod_type": "LOAD",
  "time_cap": 900,
  "order_in_competition": 7
}

### Ver WOD
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/wods/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Actualizar WOD
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/wods/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "WOD 1 - Actualizado",
  "description": "Descripcion actualizada"
}

### Agregar standard por division a WOD
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/wods/1/standards
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "division": "RX Masculino",
  "description": "Peso: 95/65 lb, Pull-ups estrictos"
}

### ============================================
### SCORES
### ============================================

### Buscar atleta para ingresar score
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/search/athlete?competition_id=1&query=Juan
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Registrar score - TIME (en segundos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scores
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "athlete_id": 1,
  "wod_id": 1,
  "raw_result": 185,
  "result_type": "completed",
  "notes": "Buen tiempo"
}

### Registrar score - TIME con cap (reps completadas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scores
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "athlete_id": 2,
  "wod_id": 1,
  "raw_result": 35,
  "result_type": "capped",
  "notes": "No termino, 35 reps"
}

### Registrar score - AMRAP (reps totales)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scores
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "athlete_id": 1,
  "wod_id": 2,
  "raw_result": 187,
  "result_type": "completed",
  "tiebreak": 45,
  "notes": "9 rondas + 7 reps"
}

### Registrar score - LOAD (peso en lbs)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scores
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "athlete_id": 1,
  "wod_id": 3,
  "raw_result": 275,
  "result_type": "completed",
  "notes": "PR personal"
}

### Registrar score bulk (multiples atletas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "wod_id": 1,
  "scores": [
    {"athlete_id": 3, "raw_result": 195, "result_type": "completed"},
    {"athlete_id": 4, "raw_result": 210, "result_type": "completed"},
    {"athlete_id": 5, "raw_result": 42, "result_type": "capped"}
  ]
}

### Ver score
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Actualizar score
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "raw_result": 180,
  "notes": "Tiempo corregido"
}

### Verificar score (admin/head judge)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/1/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Eliminar score
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### LEADERBOARD (Public)
### ============================================

### Leaderboard completo de competencia
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/1

### Leaderboard por division
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/1/division/RX%20Masculino

### Lista de divisiones
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/1/divisions

### Lista de WODs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/1/wods

### Resultados de atleta especifico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/1/athlete/1

### Resumen (top 3 por division)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leaderboard/1/summary

### ============================================
### AUDIT LOG
### ============================================

### Ver log de auditoria
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Filtrar por usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Filtrar por score
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/score/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Estadisticas de auditoria
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### EXPORT
### ============================================

### Exportar a CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/export/1/csv
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Exportar a Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/export/1/excel
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Exportar a PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/export/1/pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### EJEMPLOS DE FLUJO COMPLETO
### ============================================

### 1. Login como juez
# @name loginJudge
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=judge1&password=judge123

@judgeToken = {{loginJudge.response.body.access_token}}

### 2. Buscar atleta por numero de pechera
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scores/search/athlete?competition_id=1&query=001
Authorization: Bearer {{judgeToken}}

### 3. Registrar su score
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/scores
Authorization: Bearer {{judgeToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "athlete_id": 1,
  "wod_id": 1,
  "raw_result": 245,
  "result_type": "completed"
}
